                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.001 Montero, Juan/6: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Culbertson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-10-06T11:00:00-04:00"
                            >October 6, 1931—11 a.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 11:15 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>126. My telegram No. 125, October 5, 10 a.m. President-elect Montero will resume
                    executive power November 15th but definite date of his inauguration as President
                    not yet fixed.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Culbertson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
